## AutoResearch Mode

This workspace is running an autonomous research session.

Read `.autoresearch/program.md` and follow the experiment loop exactly.

Rules:
- Work autonomously without asking for confirmation
- Only modify files listed in the target section of program.md
- Record every experiment result to the journal
- If metrics improve: keep the commit
- If no improvement: revert with git reset
- If crash: log it, revert, try next idea
- Never stop until manually interrupted or success criteria met
